Which one of you is here?

768
00:46:34,461 --> 00:46:37,377
The poor, low IQ Arthur Fleck?

769
00:46:37,551 --> 00:46:39,684
Or The Joker, who goaded
a bunch of no-good punks...

770
00:46:39,858 --> 00:46:41,511
Do you really care?

