<i>♪ Bewitched ♪</i>

810
00:49:22,542 --> 00:49:28,026
<i>♪ Bothered and bewildered ♪</i>

811
00:49:29,592 --> 00:49:32,247
<i>♪ Am I ♪</i>

812
00:49:37,775 --> 00:49:41,909
<i>♪ Lost my heart
But what of it ♪</i>

