- <i>♪ Am I ♪</i>
- Excuse me. Yeah, thank you.

823
00:50:49,934 --> 00:50:53,241
[Paddy] <i>We'll be back
with more of Arthur Fleck</i>

824
00:50:53,415 --> 00:50:55,156
<i>after a word from our sponsors.</i>

