00:51:04,513 --> 00:51:06,124
<i>Assistant DA, Harvey Dent,</i>

828
00:51:06,298 --> 00:51:08,082
<i>is preparing his opening remarks</i>

829
00:51:08,256 --> 00:51:10,321
<i>in what some are calling,
